<section class="py-20 bg-[#eeeee6]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="section-title">初めての方へ</h2>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start justify-between">
        <!-- ステップ1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8 md:mb-0 w-full md:w-1/3 px-4">
          <div class="bg-[#00479D] text-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center">ご予約</h3>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 w-full">
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
              お電話またはLINEにて<br>ご予約ください。<br>
              <span class="font-semibold">TEL: 0985-XX-XXXX</span>
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-center">
              <a href="https://lin.ee/xxxxx" class="inline-flex items-center text-[#00479D] font-medium">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M19.365 9.89c.5 0 .905.405.905.905 0 .5-.405.905-.905.905H17.28v1.18h2.085c.5 0 .905.405.905.905 0 .5-.405.905-.905.905H16.375a.905.905 0 01-.905-.905V8.985c0-.5.405-.905.905-.905h3.075c.5 0 .905.405.905.905 0 .5-.405.905-.905.905H17.28v1.09h2.085zM11.39 15.69a.905.905 0 01-.905.905.888.888 0 01-.724-.37l-2.955-4.04v3.505c0 .5-.405.905-.905.905s-.905-.405-.905-.905V8.985c0-.5.405-.905.905-.905.29 0 .56.135.724.37l2.955 4.04V8.985c0-.5.405-.905.905-.905s.905.405.905.905v6.705zM5.37 9.89a.905.905 0 010-1.81h3.075c.5 0 .905.405.905.905v6.705c0 .5-.405.905-.905.905H5.37a.905.905 0 010-1.81h2.17v-1.54H5.37a.905.905 0 010-1.81h2.17v-1.54H5.37z"></path>
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M24 12c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0s12 5.373 12 12zM12 1.8C6.363 1.8 1.8 6.363 1.8 12c0 5.637 4.563 10.2 10.2 10.2 5.637 0 10.2-4.563 10.2-10.2 0-5.637-4.563-10.2-10.2-10.2z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                </svg>
                LINE予約はこちら
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- ステップ2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8 md:mb-0 w-full md:w-1/3 px-4 md:mt-12">
          <div class="bg-[#00479D] text-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center">カウンセリング</h3>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 w-full">
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
              症状や生活習慣など<br>詳しくお伺いします。<br>
              <span class="font-semibold">約10分程度</span>
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-center">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">※初回はカウンセリングシートにご記入いただきます</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- ステップ3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-full md:w-1/3 px-4 md:mt-24">
          <div class="bg-[#00479D] text-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center">施術</h3>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 w-full">
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
              カウンセリングに基づいた<br>オーダーメイドの施術を<br>行います。
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#00479D]">初回限定 20%OFF</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-16 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">初めての方へのお願い</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#00479D] mr-2 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>初めての方は、施術時間に加えてカウンセリング時間（約10分）が必要です。余裕をもってご来院ください。</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#00479D] mr-2 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>動きやすい服装でお越しいただくとスムーズに施術を受けていただけます。</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#00479D] mr-2 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>現在服用中のお薬がありましたら、お知らせください。</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 